hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Get a job docmed.gr But fourth and most seriously, the key proposal he announced (allowing individual trade union members to choose whether part of their political levy goes to the Labour Party in the form of an affiliation fee, rather than being automatically affiliated), while clearly right in principle, will undoubtedly increase the power of the union barons. Len McCluskey said he was “very comfortable” with what Ed Miliband is proposing. That tells you everything you need to know.
